---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy — AI Creator Stack"
  description="How AI Creator Stack collects, uses and protects your information."
  canonicalPath="/privacy-policy"
>
  <div class="container prose">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p><em>Last updated: July 2026</em></p>

    <p>
      This Privacy Policy explains how AI Creator Stack ("we", "us", "our") collects, uses and
      safeguards information when you visit <strong>theaicreatorstack.com</strong> (the "Site").
    </p>

    <h2>Information we collect</h2>
    <p>
      We collect only the information you choose to provide — for example, the name, email address
      and message you submit through our contact form. We also collect anonymous, aggregated usage
      data (such as pages visited and general location) through privacy-respecting analytics to help
      us improve the Site.
    </p>

    <h2>How we use your information</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>To respond to enquiries you send us.</li>
      <li>To understand which content is useful so we can improve it.</li>
      <li>To maintain the security and performance of the Site.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Cookies and analytics</h2>
    <p>
      The Site may use cookies and third-party analytics tools to understand how visitors use the
      Site. You can disable cookies in your browser settings at any time. Any analytics or advertising
      scripts we run are added transparently through our site settings.
    </p>

    <h2>Affiliate links</h2>
    <p>
      Some links on the Site are affiliate links. When you click one, the partner may set a cookie to
      attribute any resulting purchase to us. See our <a href="/affiliate-disclosure">Affiliate
      Disclosure</a> for more.
    </p>

    <h2>Third-party services</h2>
    <p>
      Our contact form is processed by Web3Forms, and the Site is hosted on Cloudflare. These
      providers process data on our behalf under their own privacy policies.
    </p>

    <h2>Your rights</h2>
    <p>
      You may request access to, correction of, or deletion of any personal information you've sent us
      by emailing <a href="mailto:info@theaicreatorstack.com">info@theaicreatorstack.com</a>.
    </p>

    <h2>Changes to this policy</h2>
    <p>
      We may update this policy from time to time. The "last updated" date above reflects the most
      recent revision.
    </p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
